author Al Viro <viro@www.linux.org.uk> 1114440958 -0700
committer Linus Torvalds <torvalds@ppc970.osdl.org> 1114440958 -0700

    [PATCH] ppc iomem annotations: mv643xx_eth
    
    void * __iomem replaced with intended void __iomem *.
    
    Signed-off-by: Al Viro <viro@parcelfarce.linux.theplanet.co.uk>
    Signed-off-by: Linus Torvalds <torvalds@osdl.org>

diff --git a/drivers/net/mv643xx_eth.c b/drivers/net/mv643xx_eth.c
index 7e94d45..0405e1f 100644
